a)|Surinder Singh]] #\n|[[Indian Army]]\n|<ref name=\"AC1993-2009\"/>\n|-\n|[[Naik (military rank)|Naik]]\n|[[Rambeer Singh Tomar]] #\n|[[Indian Army]]\n|<ref name=\"AC1993-2009\"/>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2001\n|\n|[[Jagdish Prasad Yadav]]#\n|\n|\n|-\n|\n|[[Matbar Singh Negi]] #\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Constable]]\n|[[Kamlesh Kumari]] #\n|[[Central Reserve Police Force|CRPF]]\n|<ref name=\"AC1993-2009\" />\n|-\n| 2000 \n|[[Major]]\n|[[Sudhir Kumar Walia]] #\n|[[Indian Army]]\n|<ref name=\"AC1993-2009\"/>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1997\n|[[Second lieutenant|Second Lieutenant]]\n|[[Puneet Nath Datt]] #\n|[[Indian Army]]\n|<ref name=\"AC1993-2009\"/>\n|-\n|[[Lieutenant colonel|Lieutenant Colonel]]\n|[[Shanti Swaroop Rana|Shanti Swarup Rana]] #\n|[[Indian Army]]\n|<ref name=\"AC1993-2009\"/>\n|-\n| 1996 \n|[[Captain]]\n|[[Arjun Singh Jasrotia|Arun Singh Jasrotia]] #\n|[[Indian Army]]\n|<ref name=\"AC1993-2009\"/>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 1995\n|[[Major]]\n|[[Rajiv Kumar Joon]] #\n|[[Indian Army]]\n|<ref name=\"AC1993-2009\"/>\n|-\n|[[Subedar]]\n|[[Sujjan Singh (soldier)|Sujjan Singh]] #\n|[[Indian Army]]\n|<ref name=\"AC1993-2009\"/>\n|-\n|[[Lieutenant colonel|Lieutenant Colonel]]\n|[[Harsh Uday Singh Gaur]] #\n|[[Indian Army]]\n|<ref name=\"AC1993-2009\"/>\n|-\n| 1994 \n|[[Colonel]]\n|[[Neelakantan Jayachandran Nair]]#\n|[[Indian Army]]\n|<ref name=\"AC1993-2009\"/>\n|-\n| 1993 \n|[[Second lieutenant|Second Lieutenant]]\n|[[Rakesh Singh (soldier)|Rakesh Singh]]#\n|[[Indian Army]]\n|<ref name=\"AC1993-2009\">{{cite web|url=http://indianarmy.nic.in/Site/FormTemplete/frmPhotoGalleryWithMenuWithTitle.aspx?MnId=Zb02lKANjvkVUclnaE1NSg%3d%3d&ParentID=xvMfYnM+Kb8YsPT0gtXYmg%3d%3d|title=Ashoka Chakra recipients (1993\u20132009)|publisher=Indian Army Web Portal|accessdate=18 January 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| 1992 \n|[[Captain]]\n|[[Sandeep Sankhla]]#\n|[[Indian Army]]\n|<ref name=\"AC1952-92\"/>\n|-\n| 1991 \n|[[Police officer|Police Officer]]\n|[[Randhir Prasad Verma]] #\n|[[Police Service]]\n|<ref 